{"tid":1821110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突然諗到件事，關於曱甴使用武力","createTime":"2020-01-12T04:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T15:57:39.000Z","uid":196227,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9d489f2e397dc6ddb1df243a815c051ca636dbdd","tid":1821110,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:25:38.000Z","msg":"我想問，班狗用任何武器之後，都應該需要寫一份報告，紀錄事件。<br />\n<br />\n咁呢方面係唔係必須？<br />\n<br />\n如果係，會唔會可以逼佢地交代有冇寫低（每1槍，每次使用狗棍）<br />\n冇既話係唔係代表佢地會濫用？<br />\n而班高層根本唔知佢地當時咩準則去使用武力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有既話，會唔會區議員/立法會議員，可以逼班狗拎出黎/強調事後文件重要性，原來任由班狗用，內部根本唔知情，純粹根據影片拆解（鳩吹）？<br />\n<br />\n可能會話班狗實攬，但係我都想大家試一試，推出議員睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91225f61f9edbd0a848cc6b735f5e47878adb89a","tid":1821110,"uid":50306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"應該開槍先要寫報告？"},{"pid":"e2d50de4e82aefd5dd96aedb79277b2fb83c8879","tid":1821110,"uid":214502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:08:21.000Z","msg":"用警棍已經要"},{"pid":"4f21acccf2864617b94f783106b3e86c58a03c8f","tid":1821110,"uid":196227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91225f61f9edbd0a848cc6b735f5e47878adb89a","tid":1821110,"uid":50306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"應該開槍先要寫報告？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:30:36.000Z","msg":"好似見過人話警棍都要"},{"pid":"eb12a35cc4190cc64b43d51ef9524e41e7fd7be8","tid":1821110,"uid":56428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"你邊個呀 攞報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7126d2903e907a7fb99fbdd780f087dc52cc4ff9","tid":1821110,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2d50de4e82aefd5dd96aedb79277b2fb83c8879","tid":1821110,"uid":214502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:08:21.000Z","msg":"用警棍已經要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:33:59.000Z","msg":"咁份報告去咗邊？<br />\n<br />\n會唔會推到有能力既人去問班狗？<br />\n<br />\n原來事後唔需要寫報告，代表濫用咗冇人知，<br />\n班狗高層都唔清楚當時狗用咩準則用用警棍，<br />\n記者會大大力屌鳩佢地鳩吹<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而如果逼到班狗一定要寫番，都可以保證佢地為咗唔寫報告而減少濫暴。"},{"pid":"6e52f74fe42b83963b0b150c06efd5d94137e714","tid":1821110,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"訓咗幾耐"},{"pid":"a2ba38c8b5942574a0f931c672018aa43bb595b9","tid":1821110,"uid":196227,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb12a35cc4190cc64b43d51ef9524e41e7fd7be8","tid":1821110,"uid":56428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"你邊個呀 攞報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:35:55.000Z","msg":"講咗叫議員質詢<br />\n睇最底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外班狗要告手足，佢地係唔係都需要拎份報告出黎？<br />\n可以透過法庭逼佢地，既然佢地要告當時人，所有細節就應該呈交？"},{"pid":"abe7b5c299424047021d436d77bdebfe5c0375e8","tid":1821110,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a2ba38c8b5942574a0f931c672018aa43bb595b9","tid":1821110,"uid":196227,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb12a35cc4190cc64b43d51ef9524e41e7fd7be8","tid":1821110,"uid":56428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"你邊個呀 攞報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:35:55.000Z","msg":"講咗叫議員質詢<br />\n睇最底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外班狗要告手足，佢地係唔係都需要拎份報告出黎？<br />\n可以透過法庭逼佢地，既然佢地要告當時人，所有細節就應該呈交？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:36:56.000Z","msg":"而家係kgb mode. 議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 議員都打呀"},{"pid":"62db76219a584422a97c2c4aea3f4c75ab0e23ad","tid":1821110,"uid":196227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6e52f74fe42b83963b0b150c06efd5d94137e714","tid":1821110,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"訓咗幾耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:39:21.000Z","msg":"呢個問題唔係我訓咗幾耐<br />\n<br />\n係我們習慣咗幾多<br />\n<br />\n點解從來都唔針對任何細節去搞，雖然唔係我落手做，我唔知當中幾困難，但係我純粹想帶個意識，我們唔可以習慣。<br />\n<br />\n況且區選大勝，我們手牌大咗，從事呢方面都比較易<br />\n可以叫當時人去搵當區區議員，之後有籍口介入，再實行之後既事"},{"pid":"153f24cdd67ad4337feced5d2ac17e8f4e833e84","tid":1821110,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"abe7b5c299424047021d436d77bdebfe5c0375e8","tid":1821110,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a2ba38c8b5942574a0f931c672018aa43bb595b9","tid":1821110,"uid":196227,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb12a35cc4190cc64b43d51ef9524e41e7fd7be8","tid":1821110,"uid":56428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"你邊個呀 攞報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:35:55.000Z","msg":"講咗叫議員質詢<br />\n睇最底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外班狗要告手足，佢地係唔係都需要拎份報告出黎？<br />\n可以透過法庭逼佢地，既然佢地要告當時人，所有細節就應該呈交？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:36:56.000Z","msg":"而家係kgb mode. 議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 議員都打呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"但係永遠都唔捉實，細節部份都唔追究。<br />\n由班狗出武器嗰刻，就需要寫報告，你係當事人，問佢拎份報告了解被使用武力防止之後。 咁樣ok?"},{"pid":"3fdd7843fb649286b6277fe95fdc06fdea3d0431","tid":1821110,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用警棍已經要</blockquote>咁份報告去咗邊？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會唔會推到有能力既人去問班狗？</span><br />\n<br />\n原來事後唔需要寫報告，代表濫用咗冇人知，<br />\n班狗高層都唔清楚當時狗用咩準則用用警棍，<br />\n記者會大大力屌鳩佢地鳩吹<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而如果逼到班狗一定要寫番，都可以保證佢地為咗唔寫報告而減少濫暴。</blockquote><br />\n行動細節不適合公開 否則會影響行動部置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e437b12385640df12b22f4c38f7e3c7f9737bc3","tid":1821110,"uid":285371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"事實你有道理<br />\n但已經police state 左半年<br />\n佢就係咩都唔比<br />\n連名都無啊。。。<br />\n醫院搞呀伯可以保留提供不在場證據權利"},{"pid":"832b531eb87a2460b865faea0188273726c207d0","tid":1821110,"uid":196227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3fdd7843fb649286b6277fe95fdc06fdea3d0431","tid":1821110,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用警棍已經要</blockquote>咁份報告去咗邊？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會唔會推到有能力既人去問班狗？</span><br />\n<br />\n原來事後唔需要寫報告，代表濫用咗冇人知，<br />\n班狗高層都唔清楚當時狗用咩準則用用警棍，<br />\n記者會大大力屌鳩佢地鳩吹<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而如果逼到班狗一定要寫番，都可以保證佢地為咗唔寫報告而減少濫暴。</blockquote><br />\n行動細節不適合公開 否則會影響行動部置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"唔係行動細節，係當時使用武力準則，要大大力追住屌。<br />\n唔好比人耍完就算。"},{"pid":"84db237121a200f8a568de6d0f98e8e4a27019e1","tid":1821110,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e437b12385640df12b22f4c38f7e3c7f9737bc3","tid":1821110,"uid":285371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"事實你有道理<br />\n但已經police state 左半年<br />\n佢就係咩都唔比<br />\n連名都無啊。。。<br />\n醫院搞呀伯可以保留提供不在場證據權利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:44:26.000Z","msg":"就係點解我們要習慣。<br />\n<br />\n我啱啱發現咗一件事<br />\n連登滲透好撚耐，我呢個post純粹學術性<br />\n即刻比4個負評，係唔係班狗驚寫報告？"},{"pid":"e0a68012a58b850535b3df26353d224ad87d0bec","tid":1821110,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:44:43.000Z","msg":"同獨裁講拳頭。 唔係講道理"},{"pid":"6efd5233f5ddd7ecab4b589e12423d3c20ba108d","tid":1821110,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"832b531eb87a2460b865faea0188